{"tid":2397584,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"謝霆鋒音樂","createTime":"2021-02-06T14:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T03:52:08.000Z","uid":108756,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ff62ae181288782dc2060c6a5bda7f7bda353491","tid":2397584,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"其實講真佢又唔係真係完全唔識彈<br />\n唔明點解好時佢支結他都要較到咁細聲 掃chord唔使太大聲我明 但solo個啲佢又唔係彈唔到 睇返好多舊時live佢識彈彈到 但就一定係細聲到蚊滋咁 佢又唔似係咁無信心同自卑<br />\n同埋咁耐以黎大家笑得佢最多既其實咪只係viva單線solo<br />\n而笑既原因其實都不外乎因為一段其實咁簡單既solo佢好似可以靠呢段黎成為佢最自豪既音樂咁 而佢仲覺得無問題其實咁<br />\n如果當年佢真係專注只做音樂同歌手 同埋真係去咪結他咪樂理<br />\n佢創作未別會去到日本樂隊或者周杰倫咁多元咁破格<br />\n但至少行出黎攞起支結他係真材實料<br />\n如果佢真係一路行歌手條路佢今日會有咩成就<br />\n不過其實佢零四年開始佢啲歌都開始走下坡把聲都無廿歲個陣咁厚同入咪<br />\n不過無可否認佢好多時俾人感覺佢攞住支結他只係想型<br />\n理性討論<br />\n利申鋒迷<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h31cE-yl4Vs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh31cE-yl4Vs&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMISWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=d8df5407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h31cE-yl4Vs</a><br />\n2:15<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IYl-6jTyn9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIYl-6jTyn9I&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMISWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=6a0235fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IYl-6jTyn9I</a><br />\n2:34<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1RyMuI7o-_Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1RyMuI7o-_Q&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMISWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=17267254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1RyMuI7o-_Q</a> 佢呢場廿年前唱得好聽好多好過早排係中國唱個幾次<br />\n3:55<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eRHwghXt22c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeRHwghXt22c&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMISWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=402d2172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eRHwghXt22c</a><br />\n3:38<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SVPWdbMkrzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSVPWdbMkrz